  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">Social Proof for Life Insurance Agents</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">Life insurance is one of the hardest trust sales in existence. Clients are buying something they hope never to use, for a benefit they'll never personally receive, from someone they just met. Client testimonials that speak to your guidance, honesty, and long-term relationship turn a skeptical prospect into a signed policy and a referral source.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Convert cold prospects into confident clients</h2>
      <p>Most people don't seek out a life insurance agent — they respond to one. When your website demonstrates that previous clients found you honest, clear, and genuinely caring about their family's future, you become the agent people want to work with rather than the one they need to work with. That difference drives referrals for years.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What clients say that builds your book of business</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
