        <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> "Explained every policy in plain English. No jargon, no pressure. First agent I've ever actually understood."</li>
        <li><strong>Long-term care:</strong> "Annual review every year for 8 years, adjusting our coverage as our family changed. This is what an agent should be."</li>
        <li><strong>Claims support:</strong> "When my husband passed, he handled everything with the insurance company. I didn't have to deal with any of it during the hardest time of my life."</li>
        <li><strong>Referrals:</strong> "I've sent four friends to him. All of them called to thank me. That's how good he is."</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for insurance agents</h2>
